   identification of offensive language and hate speech, an important
   problem in social media. In this paper, we present fBERT, a BERT model
   retrained on SOLID, the largest English offensive language
   identification corpus available with over 1:4 million offensive
   instances. We evaluate fBERT's performance on identifying offensive
